Source: https://github.com/catdad/canvas-confetti

Vendored for spec 011 (Warm-Modern Facelift) per FR-016 / FR-050 — single
celebratory-motion-library carve-out, ≤ 5 KB gzipped.

NOTE: The actual canvas-confetti.min.js binary MUST be placed in this directory
by an operator with network access. The _SigningCeremony partial calls into
window.confetti only inside an IsFresh check, so absence of the script means
no confetti fires (graceful degradation). Documented in
specs/011-warm-modern-facelift/implementation-notes.md.
